        <ab>SACRED</ab>
        <ab>TO THE MEMORY OF</ab>
        <ab>ELIZABETH CHARLOTTE</ab>
        <ab>WIDOW OF R.F. HODGSON ESQ B.C.S.</ab>
        <ab>WHO DIED IN ROME 19.FEB.1882</ab>
        <ab>AETAT.64</ab>
        <ab/>
        <ab>THIS MONUMENT IS ERECTED IN LOVING REMEMBRANCE</ab>
        <ab>BY HER SON AND DAUGHTER</ab>
        <ab/>
        <ab>I HAVE LOVED THEE WITH AN EVERLASTING LOVE</ab>
        <ab>THEREFORE WITH LOVING KINDNESS HAVE I DRAWN THEE</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignr">
          <emph>Jer.XXXI 3</emph>
        </ab>
        <ab>IN THY PRESENCE FULNESS OF JOY</ab>
        <ab rend="Alignr">
          <emph>PS. XVI II.</emph>
        </ab>
      </div>
